summary: The 23rd century is a century that lasts from January 1, 2201, to December 31, 2300.
full_text: The 23rd century will be the century of the Common Era which, in the Gregorian calendar, will begin on January 1, 2201, and end on December 31, 2300. It is distinct from the century known as the 2200s, which will begin on January 1, 2200 and will end on December 31, 2299.
title: 23rd century
